  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This programme builds the capacity to communicate research. Researcher Connect has been developed to support this. It involves a series of facetoface training modules, delivered by experienced trainers and backed up with online resources.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To build the communication skills of researchers in partner countries. Target: 160 researchers (8 trainings) directly trained for the first year in 5 region of Thailand.</narrative>
